<Layout title="Understanding Bitcoin Supply: Why Only 21 Million Coins Exist" description="Explore Bitcoin's fixed 21 million supply cap — how it works, how many coins are left, and why scarcity drives the network's value proposition." keywords="bitcoin supply, 21 million bitcoin, bitcoin scarcity, how many bitcoin left, bitcoin max supply, bitcoin circulation, bitcoin lost coins">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <article class="prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose">
